BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 586.50 Td (Docker Desktop for Windows - AMD64) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 565.88 Td (Do not choose Windows ARM64 unless the machine has an ARM CPU.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 541.38 Td (A2. Install Docker Desktop) Tj ET
